narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A pretty relaxed class where you work towards a final project at the end of the semester, and do readings throughout. Take it if Martin is teaching, as he will lead a class that is at once fun and thought provoking.

This class provoked thoughtful discussion. Helped me develop into a more thoughtful artist. I wish there had been more required projects than just one. In class activities were interesting. Some days were a little haphazard. Very supportive cooperative environment.

i would absolutely recommend this course! it was a refreshing course that i looked forward to every week and will miss so much now that it's over. it is very self-directed and we have ample time to develop an idea and work through it. this self-directed project is supplemented with excellent readings and exercises that really improved the way i think and talk about art and making.

Yes I would recommend this course to students who want to do their own sculpture project based on their own interests. It's a good chance for a student to carefully think about his ideas, and after distilling his ideas, he can produce a more thoroughly thought work.
